WEBVTT

00:00:01.753 --> 00:00:02.920
Cancer.

00:00:03.301 --> 00:00:06.366
Many of us have lost family,
friends or loved ones

00:00:06.390 --> 00:00:08.070
to this horrible disease.

00:00:08.094 --> 00:00:10.190
I know there are some of you
in the audience

00:00:10.214 --> 00:00:11.455
who are cancer survivors,

00:00:11.479 --> 00:00:13.634
or who are fighting cancer at this moment.

00:00:13.658 --> 00:00:15.649
My heart goes out to you.

00:00:15.673 --> 00:00:20.947
While this word often conjures up
emotions of sadness and anger and fear,

00:00:20.971 --> 00:00:24.485
I bring you good news
from the front lines of cancer research.

00:00:24.509 --> 00:00:28.369
The fact is, we are starting to win
the war on cancer.

